* keep the layout vertically compact
* do not make the hero too tall
* prioritize showing selection UI early
* ensure result cards stay readable at smaller widths
* use clean card-based layout
* preserve strong spacing consistency
* keep the overall tone friendly, simple, and practical
* avoid overly playful or decorative UI patterns

